Contact! (February 14, 2009)
Sources: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BfH-QsojiLc

Start the quest by talking to the High Priest of Icthlarin in the south-west temple of Sophanem. 

High Priest: "Good day, <playername>"
Player: "Hello there. How goes the fight for Klenter's soul?"
High Priest: "It never ends; as soon as I think we have it won, The Devourer catches us off our guard again."
Player: "I wish you luck in your attempts."
High Priest: "Likewise, <playername>, in your adventures."
Player: "What plans have you for the future of the town?"
High Priest: "You have proved that the plagues aren't contagious, so we must try to lift the quarantine that Menaphos has imposed on us."
Player: "So, what are you going to do?"
High Priest: "I don't have a clue. I've tried to meet with them and we were rebuffed in a most unpleasant fashion."
Player: "Perhaps I could help?"
High Priest: "I have a feeling this could prove a somewhat hazardous quest for you and I'm not even sure where you would start. However, if you are happy dealing with our woes, we would, of course, be grateful."
